OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,FSchools in Northern Ireland have been
OL,7,Fasked to take "any and all actions
OL,8,Fpossible to reduce expenditure" amid a
OL,9,Ffunding crisis.
OL,11,FEducation Authority (EA) chief
OL,12,Fexecutive Richard Pengelly has written
OL,13,Fto all principals and chairs of boards
OL,14,Fof school governors in the region,
OL,15,Fasking them to take measures including
OL,16,Frestricting the use of substitute
OL,17,Fcover.
