OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,FIn a letter, the EA, which manages
OL,7,Fschools in Northern Ireland, says it
OL,8,Fis facing a funding shortfall of
OL,9,Faround #300 million.
OL,11,FMr Pengelly said the education sector
OL,12,Fis living "with the consequences of
OL,13,Fyears of increasingly unmanageable
OL,14,Ffunding shortfalls".
OL,16,FHe said: "The warnings about this
OL,17,Fyear's budget that were made publicly
OL,18,Fby the Department (of Education) and
OL,19,Fothers are sadly being borne out by
OL,20,Fevents.
OL,26,@tD@KOUvD@SO]xD@JOU
