OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"At this juncture, EA is currently
OL,7,Freporting a funding gap of c#300m and,
OL,8,Funlike the position in previous years,
OL,9,Fwe have been advised that no further
OL,10,Fsignificant funding allocations are
OL,11,Flikely to be made available to address
OL,12,Fthis shortfall.
OL,14,F"We are therefore currently on a
OL,15,Ftrajectory towards a significant
OL,16,Foverspend at year end."
OL,18,FHe added: "In that context, it is
OL,19,Fcritical that school leaders seek to
OL,20,Ftake any and all actions possible to
OL,21,Freduce expenditure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@WO]zD@KOU
