OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"This should include, among other
OL,7,Fissues, not proceeding with
OL,8,Fdiscretionary spend, minimise, as far
OL,9,Fas possible, entering into new
OL,10,Ffinancial commitments related to
OL,11,Fappointments, and restricting the use
OL,12,Fof substitute cover."
OL,14,FMr Pengelly said the EA and Department
OL,15,Fof Education are working together in
OL,16,Fseeking to identify a range of
OL,17,Fstrategic measures to reduce costs.
