OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,FHe added that the EA "cannot ignore
OL,7,Fthe reality that all schools'
OL,8,Fexpenditure impacts on the overall
OL,9,Feducation sector financial position".
OL,11,FThe letter said: "Specifically, the
OL,12,Fuse by schools of any accumulated
OL,13,Fsurpluses is unfunded, and would be an
OL,14,Fadditional pressure on the EA budget.
OL,16,F"Therefore, I am asking you to ensure
OL,17,Fthat a rigorous approach is taken to
OL,18,Fall spending decisions within your
OL,19,Fschools, and to take all reasonable
OL,20,Fsteps to contain expenditure where
OL,21,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@VOUqD@dO]sD@ROUxD@AOU
