OL,3,CEducation Authority urges schools to
OL,4,Ccut spending amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"Approval to incur expenditure should
OL,7,Fonly be given to the highest priority
OL,8,Fand inescapable requests.
OL,10,F"I regret having to make this request
OL,11,Fbut, given the scale of the financial
OL,12,Fpressures this year, I trust you
OL,13,Funderstand that we must all play our
OL,14,Fpart."
